citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"其實哩句口號既意思唔重要<br />\n哩句口號本身都唔重要<br />\n重點係五大訴求 係普選"},{"pid":"71b84a74789d09cd39a8209edeb360c0b22e3caa","tid":1424220,"uid":265662,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"文宣洗地"},{"pid":"a6a8207425f6b40a7d41bf384c50c57aedfdaed4","tid":1424220,"uid":95221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"都ok"},{"pid":"953f55697f114a3bead7c806acfa7130b667f8f0","tid":1424220,"uid":279616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"#罷工罷巿罷買<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港三罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"993b135fa47ecb2e00024c3e6035d2f40df46eea","tid":1424220,"uid":60916,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"毛ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當年係你做泛民大粒野你話幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ff1c8b434fc1e4943764e600ee541f4410b51c","tid":1424220,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830cd8253ade8f3278fa3492776de7a926eef74b","tid":1424220,"uid":271407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550614f9f5ae845b12690298fedb92a8b3feb4f1","tid":1424220,"uid":294376,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"其實大家一定冇議員咁熟政府既狗招<br />\n呢啲就叫做政治智慧 同市民行動派結合<br />\n力量可以好大"},{"pid":"1fd8a68f0673f6499a866b5ed9ea90c834a21204","tid":1424220,"uid":2923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"有巴打用類比方法俾D廢老更容易知道同理解,其實類比手法都好"},{"pid":"86a73c35a70b26963fdafbc8590305c43e604c49","tid":1424220,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"【簡單易明文宣】光復香港 時代革命 背後意思<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423860</a><br />\n<br />\n值得參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5040d8ee4e56b995067e4b9aee729e3b8bb8b2","tid":1424220,"uid":237517,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"佢無講錯 革命係由下而上既改革<br />\n<br />\n而家警黑勾結 政府腐敗 正係需要反黑反暴光復香港既革命"},{"pid":"43f1646fa7e7370e027e6cc964ed0d7c0ef15638","tid":1424220,"uid":15371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c308c750831013cc7d7269208e573725b0fd2a5","tid":1424220,"uid":32525,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"李怡果個最好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"李怡講乜 有冇關鍵字/link"},{"pid":"62d905a7022fda2a34311448477385959f39c673","tid":1424220,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:04:58.000Z","msg":"重溫 616, 71, 721 宣言, 文宣請加油, 令我們的行動合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423473</a>"},{"pid":"b86d83ed8c023ece33cabce0eaafe5b090188450","tid":1424220,"uid":37232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:09:11.000Z","msg":"重溫 616, 71, 721 宣言, 文宣請加油, 令我們的行動合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423473</a><br />\n<br />\n其中一個方向係<br />\n正名「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n光復香港 = 回復以往繁榮既香港<br />\n方法: 首4大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n<br />\n時代革命=香港體制要改革<br />\n方法: 第五大訴求<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n而唔係林鄭所誤解既港獨<br />\n<br />\n建議之一, 請其他巴打更改"},{"pid":"168a2337bc9bade472251203370f2db31fbccb09","tid":1424220,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:27:12.000Z","msg":"呢個解釋應該最得民心"},{"pid":"cc82e193477e0b95483bf9f45b950126892923a3","tid":1424220,"uid":128923,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"993b135fa47ecb2e00024c3e6035d2f40df46eea","tid":1424220,"uid":60916,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"毛ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當年係你做泛民大粒野你話幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:29:45.000Z","msg":"佢有講魚蛋個時佢係英國參加婚禮<br />\n佢落機個時泛民已經割左席 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好似係最關心天琦既議員 成日去探佢"},{"pid":"4f98b39be4840e36324593740636adb850857e8c","tid":1424220,"uid":216426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:36:16.000Z","msg":"勇武有勇武做 <br />\n我地點做 唔關你班和理非事<br />\n唔需要你地勸交、叫停人<br />\n<br />\n同樣地你地和理非點做<br />\n你地既事<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街冷氣軍師咪撚再叫停人<br />\n各有各做 唔係一個口號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1425473/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1425473/page/1</a><br />\npush"},{"pid":"d3bdb058f9e9861b2c19fac6dddc863c3f930891","tid":1424220,"uid":112221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:27:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d7871ddf2145c0c8471d0f3dcf45c6037995534","tid":1424220,"uid":116625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,