q風波無割游b baggio眾志𥱊<br />\n呢件事記一世"},{"pid":"dc6458debf0c061674f4f1fadf402eb60f7f6316","tid":1424220,"uid":289191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:45:35.000Z","msg":"共產黨唔畀人嗌&quot;光復香港 時代革命&quot; <br />\n主要係唔想梁天琦成為運動的icon<br />\n天琦坐緊冤獄<br />\n共產黨無辦法統戰或抹黑天琦<br />\n唯有玩分化<br />\n香港民主運動幾十年都欠缺一個<br />\n結合理論，行動與道德的icon<br />\n天琦在這一刻團結了香港人<br />\n放棄&quot;光復香港 時代革命&quot; 就等如再一次陷害天琦"},{"pid":"075da7a9d1f4dee194df97d1eafc46e70b6a070b","tid":1424220,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:46:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"cac1733227974f69cfde3a0a4a05f95ed58625ed","tid":1424220,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"推 支持毛姨"},{"pid":"aa1d0d1dbe5cae68faf261db02adc2c3dd197074","tid":1424220,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0c6d21fb9efad1c57a8774c449bd070002fa0b3","tid":1424220,"uid":260037,"like":215,"dislike":0,"score":215,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"各人有唔同睇法 但作為議員 佢呢個解釋係得體得黎亦對抗爭者有利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"好幫手啦"},{"pid":"e055cc0ec6c7de2cec66de7895ad5607b96a28a9","tid":1424220,"uid":279938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"各自解讀 暗渡陳倉"},{"pid":"a965f10193a702cc042c619afb9d0ad723247a17","tid":1424220,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9343bbd060f8042b268488b0a546635d5315921","tid":1424220,"uid":105532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:56:11.000Z","msg":"毛EE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b6cdaf98c009241