r />\n佢落機個時泛民已經割左席 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好似係最關心天琦既議員 成日去探佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:45:34.000Z","msg":"毛e當年dq風波無割游b baggio眾志𥱊<br />\n呢件事記一世"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"有冇source<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%9F%E9%9D%9C+%E6%B8%B8%E6%85%A7&amp;rlz=1CDGOYI_enTW604TW604&amp;oq=%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%9F%E9%9D%9C+%E6%B8%B8%E6%85%A7&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57.12735j0j9&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sourceid=chrome-mobile&amp;ie=UTF-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25E6%25AF%259B%25E5%25AD%259F%25E9%259D%259C%2B%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%2585%25A7%26rlz%3D1CDGOYI_enTW604TW604%26oq%3D%25E6%25AF%259B%25E5%25AD%259F%25E9%259D%259C%2B%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%2585%25A7%26aqs%3Dchrome..69i57.12735j0j9%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26sourceid%3Dchrome-mobile%26ie%3DUTF-8&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=8a40f08f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%9F%E9%9D%9C+%E6%B8%B8%E6%85%A7&amp;rlz=1CDGOYI_enTW604TW604&amp;oq=%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%9F%E9%9D%9C+%E6%B8%B8%E6%85%A7&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57.12735j0j9&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sourceid=chrome-mobile&amp;ie=UTF-8</a>"},{"pid":"6301f1da1f7aeea046f48790c802f84c89bc9f3a","tid":1424220,"uid":111899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"欣賞佢唔係淨係識叫人改口號<br />\n而係幫手解釋"},{"pid":"3dbbb1358f6bd9e589e8ce56fd1b0728d7f2532c","tid":1424220,"uid":32525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f90eb46d558a60092faa68d28e7914ac1ed9eb42","tid":1424220,"uid":2446,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e414e30c753dc53c7dbeda96e95555dd54db219","tid":1424220,"uid":32525,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"43f1646fa7e7370e027e6cc964ed0d7c0ef15638","tid":1424220,"uid":15371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"李怡講乜 有冇關鍵字/link"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:17:45.000Z","msg":"但「光復香港」我們都知道要「光復」到甚麼時代，不就是人權有保障、市民有法律權利、警察是保護市民而不是向自由表達意見的市民施暴的香港嗎？打出港英旗也好，打出美國旗也罷，重點都不是呼喚英國美國來統治香港，而是表示香港要回到英美體制中對自由、對人權的保護。<br />\n<br />\n「時代革命」是革甚麼命？革命的定義就是尋求根本性的改變。革命不一定是改朝換代，不一定是暴力與流血。工業革命，技術革命也是革命。文化大革命是在原有朝代中進行，辛亥革命實際上暴力與流血不多，有史家認為暴力與流血比日本的明治維新還少。香港的「時代革命」，就是要把被中共港共徹底破壞了的一國兩制、港人治港作根本性的改變。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民本來沒有想到要作這樣根本性改變的，但7.21讓我們覺得香港變成黑社會統治了，於是即使在和理非的示威中，也喊出了梁天琦2016年的口號：「光復香港，時代革命」！事情的變質是由元朗事件引起的。<br />\n<br />\n李怡：光復香港　時代革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420821</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"毛姨姨嗰個解釋一句精闢講完<br />\n對於弱智人士黎講 你比一邊文佢睇 佢會話你搞屎棍<br />\n一句講完佢load唔到就冇野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"佢篇文咁寫姐，李怡都係一句，光復返法治香港，亦解通721後先有呢句口號"},{"pid":"ae5ad7bb0935794d3fdb1c7554f619692f7c91cc","tid":1424220,"uid":53016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"毛姨姨講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9671b116d596453968d139c42ea7b56ffee24a2","tid":1424220,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14d1a1febddef70bc49ef0f748a547c99f183f3a","tid":1424220,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc4cc74ef8dc4d87da45bed8970a90210dbdca9","tid":1424220,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8671ad7864dec03f8d7613f5c50336a56f1e1625","tid":1424220,"uid":11062,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:45:34.000Z","msg":"毛e當年dq風波無割游b baggio眾志𥱊<br />\n呢件事記一世"},"citedBy":2,"replyTim